#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An additional option in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu allows to "
"define if the tools draw with anti-aliasing (default) or not."
msgstr ""
"Dodatna možnost v meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> omogoča določitev, "
"ali orodja rišejo z izravnavanjem (privzeto) ali ne."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acquiring Screenshots"
msgstr "Pridobivanje posnetkov zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <quote>screenshot</quote> is a snapshot of what is on your computer's "
"screen. It can be useful to explain some actions that should be done to "
"obtain the result, or to show the issue that you have found."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Posnetek zaslona</quote> je posnetek tega, kar je na zaslonu vašega "
"računalnika. Koristno je lahko razložiti nekaj dejanj, ki jih je treba "
"izvesti, da dobite rezultat, ali prikazati težavo, ki ste jo našli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make screenshot ready for editing in &kolourpaint; window you can use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Acquire Screenshot</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> item from &kolourpaint; main menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite posnetek zaslona pripraviti za urejanje v &kolourpaint; lahko "
"uporabite element <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pridobi posnetek zaslona</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz glavnega "
"menija &kolourpaint;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the opened dialog you can change <guilabel>Screenshot Delay</guilabel> "
"(in seconds), and choose to <guilabel>Hide Main Window</guilabel> during "
"screenshotting. When you are ready to take a screenshot just click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>. The screenshot taken will be placed directly into "
"the &kolourpaint; editing area."
msgstr ""
"V odprtem pogovornem oknu lahko spremenite <guilabel>Zakasnitev posnetka</"
"guilabel> (v sekundah) in izberete <guilabel>Skrij glavno okno</guilabel> "
"med snemanjem zaslona. Ko ste pripravljeni narediti posnetek zaslona, ​​"
"kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>. Posnetek zaslona bo postavljen "
"neposredno v območje urejanja &kolourpaint;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tool Reference"
msgstr "Referenca orodja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A quick way to select a tool in &kolourpaint; is to press the single key "
"shortcut associated with it, documented below and in the <interface>Tool "
"Box</interface> tooltips. You can also hold <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"&Shift;</keycombo> while pressing the key, which is necessary when you are "
"writing text (as the single key shortcuts will be disabled). For example, to "
"select the brush, press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo> or just B (when not writing text)."
msgstr ""
"Hiter način za izbiro orodja v &kolourpaint; je, da pritisnete z njim "
"povezano bližnjico z eno tipko, dokumentirano spodaj in v opisih orodij "
"<interface>Škatla z orodjem</interface>. Med pritiskom tipke lahko tudi "
"držite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;</keycombo>, kar je nujno, ko "
"pišete besedilo (ker bodo bližnjice z eno tipko onemogočene). Če želite na "
"primer izbrati čopič, pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;"
"<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> ali samo B (ko ne pišete besedila)."

