#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brush"
msgstr "Čopič"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click or click and drag with the brush to draw."
msgstr "Kliknite ali kliknite in povlecite s čopičem za risanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the shapes to select the brush shape. You can use a "
"circular, square, slash or backslash brush shape."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na eno od oblik, da izberete obliko čopiča. Uporabite lahko "
"okroglo, kvadratno, poševno ali poševno obliko čopiča."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431 index.docbook:484 index.docbook:619 index.docbook:671
#: index.docbook:809
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &LMB; draws in the foreground color. The &RMB; draws in the background "
"color."
msgstr "&LMB; riše v barvi ospredja. &RMB; nariše v barvi ozadja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Picker"
msgstr "Izbirnik barv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set the foreground color, <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on a "
"pixel. To set the background color, <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click "
"on a pixel. &kolourpaint; will then return to the previously selected tool."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti barvo ospredja, <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> kliknite "
"slikovno piko. Če želite nastaviti barvo ozadja, <mousebutton>desno</"
"mousebutton> kliknite slikovno piko. &kolourpaint; se nato vrne na predhodno "
"izbrano orodje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connected Lines and Polygon"
msgstr "Povezane črte in mnogokotnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to draw connected lines. The polygon tool is used in the same "
"way, however, the start and end points are automatically connected to form a "
"polygon."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite in povlecite, da narišete povezane črte. Orodje za poligon se "
"uporablja na enak način, vendar sta začetna in končna točka samodejno "
"povezani v poligon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &LMB; draws in the foreground color. The &RMB; draws in the background "
"color, and will also reverse the fill color for polygons."
msgstr ""
"&LMB; riše v barvi ospredja. &RMB; nariše barvo ozadja in obrne tudi barvo "
"polnila za poligone."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can <link linkend=\"tool-options\">set the line width</link>. For "
"polygons, you can also <link linkend=\"tool-options\">set the fill style</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Lahko <link linkend=\"tool-options\">nastavite širino črte</link>. Za "
"poligone lahko tudi <link linkend=\"tool-options\">nastavite slog polnila</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Curve"
msgstr "Krivulja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to draw a line - this sets the start and end points. You can "
"set up to two control points by dragging. To finish the curve without using "
"both or any control points, click the other mouse button. The curve tool "
"draws a Cubic Bezier."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite in povlecite, da narišete črto - to nastavi začetno in končno "
"točko. Z vlečenjem lahko nastavite do dve kontrolni točki. Če želite končati "
"krivuljo brez uporabe obeh ali katere koli kontrolne točke, kliknite drugi "
"gumb miške. Orodje za krivulje nariše Bezierovo kubično krivuljo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:487 index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can also <link linkend=\"tool-options\">set the line width</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko <link linkend=\"tool-options\">nastavite širino črte</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ellipse"
msgstr "Elipsa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click and drag to draw an ellipse."
msgstr "Kliknite in povlecite, da narišete elipso."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:502 index.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &LMB; draws in the foreground color. The &RMB; draws in the background "
"color, and will reverse the fill color."
msgstr ""
"&LMB; riše v barvi ospredja. &RMB; nariše barvo ozadja in obrne barvo "
"polnila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:505 index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also <link linkend=\"tool-options\">set the line width and fill "
"style</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko <link linkend=\"tool-options\">nastavite širino črte in slog "
"polnila</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:508 index.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid "For additional functionality, use the modifier keys:"
msgstr "Za dodatne funkcije uporabite modifikacijske tipke:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hold &Shift; and drag to draw a circle."
msgstr "Držite &Shift; in povlecite, da narišete krog."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To draw an ellipse with a center point of your choice, hold &Ctrl;, click on "
"the center point, and drag until the ellipse is the correct size and shape."
msgstr ""
"Če želite narisati elipso s središčno točko po vaši izbiri, držite &Ctrl;, "
"kliknite središčno točko in povlecite, dokler ni elipsa pravilne velikosti "
"in oblike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To draw a circle with a center point of your choice, hold &Ctrl; and "
"&Shift;, click on the center point, and drag until the circle is the correct "
"size."
msgstr ""
"Če želite narisati krog s središčem po vaši izbiri, držite &Ctrl; in "
"&Shift;, kliknite središčno točko in povlecite, dokler krog ni pravilne "
"velikosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Erasers"
msgstr "Radirke"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Eraser"
msgstr "Radirka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click and drag with the eraser to rub out mistakes."
msgstr "Kliknite in povlecite z radirko, da zbrišete napake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unlike other tools, the erasers draw in the background color. To draw in the "
"foreground color, use the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Za razliko od drugih orodij radirke rišejo v barvi ozadja. Za risanje v "
"barvi ospredja uporabite &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The eraser only has <link linkend=\"tool-options\">square shapes</link>. To "
"draw with other shapes such as circles use the <link linkend=\"tool-brush"
"\">Brush</link> and the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Radirka ima samo <link linkend=\"tool-options\">kvadratne oblike</link>. Za "
"risanje z drugimi oblikami, kot so krogi, uporabite <link linkend=\"tool-"
"brush\">čopič</link> in &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click on the Eraser icon to clear the entire image. This is "
"equivalent to using the <link linkend=\"image-clear\">Clear</link> option on "
"the Image menu."
msgstr ""
"Dvokliknite ikono radirke, da počistite celotno sliko. To je enakovredno "
"uporabi možnosti <link linkend=\"image-clear\">Počisti</link> v meniju Slika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Eraser"
msgstr "Barvna radirka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to replace pixels of the foreground color with the background "
"color. To replace all pixels similar (but not necessarily exactly equal) to "
"the foreground color, such as in dithered images and photos, use a <link "
"linkend=\"color-box\">Color Similarity</link> setting other than Exact."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite in povlecite, da zamenjate slikovne pike barve ospredja z barvo "
"ozadja. Če želite zamenjati vse slikovne pike, ki so podobne (vendar ne "
"nujno popolnoma enake) barvi ospredja, na primer na slikah in fotografijah z "
"mešanjem, uporabite nastavitev <link linkend=\"color-box\">Podobnost barv</"
"link>, ki ni Natančna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unlike other tools, the erasers draw in the background color. To replace "
"pixels of the background color with the foreground color, use the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Za razliko od drugih orodij radirke rišejo v barvi ozadja. Če želite "
"slikovne pike barve ozadja zamenjati z barvo ospredja, uporabite &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the <link linkend=\"tool-options\">eraser size</link>."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko <link linkend=\"tool-options\">velikost radirke</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Double-click on the Color Eraser icon to apply it to the entire image."
msgstr "Dvokliknite ikono barvne radirke, da jo uporabite za celotno sliko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flood Fill"
msgstr "Zapolnitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click to fill a region. To fill a dithered region, use a <link linkend="
"\"color-box\">Color Similarity</link> setting other than Exact."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite za zapolnitev regije. Če želite zapolniti zamegljeno območje, "
"uporabite nastavitev <link linkend=\"color-box\">Podobnost barv</link>, ki "
"ni Natančno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &LMB; fills in the foreground color. The &RMB; fills in the background "
"color."
msgstr "&LMB; zapolni barvo ospredja. &RMB; zapolni barvo ozadja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line"
msgstr "Črta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click and drag to draw a line."
msgstr "Kliknite in povlecite, da narišete črto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hold &Ctrl; to draw lines angled at the nearest multiple of 30 degrees - "
"these are the lines in the red diagram."
msgstr ""
"Držite &Ctrl; za risanje črt pod kotom najbližjega večkratnika 30 stopinj - "
"to so črte v rdečem diagramu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hold &Shift; to draw lines angled at the nearest multiple of 45 degrees - "
"these are the lines in the blue diagram."
msgstr ""
"Držite &Shift; za risanje črt pod kotom najbližjega večkratnika 45 stopinj - "
"to so črte v modrem diagramu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hold &Ctrl; and &Shift; to draw lines angled at the nearest multiple of 30 "
"or 45 degrees - these are the lines in the green diagram."
msgstr ""
"Držite &Ctrl; in &Shift; za risanje črt pod kotom najbližjega večkratnika 30 "
"ali 45 stopinj - to so črte v zelenem diagramu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Pen</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pero</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click to draw a dot or click and drag to draw a freehand line."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite, da narišete piko, ali kliknite in povlecite, da narišete "
"prostoročno črto."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rectangles"
msgstr "Pravokotniki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to draw a rectangle. The Rounded Rectangle is a Rectangle "
"with rounded corners."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite in povlecite, da narišete pravokotnik. Zaobljeni pravokotnik je "
"pravokotnik z zaobljenimi vogali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hold &Shift; and drag to draw a square."
msgstr "Držite &Shift; in povlecite, da narišete kvadrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To draw a rectangle with a center point of your choice, hold &Ctrl;, click "
"on the center point, and drag until the rectangle is the correct size and "
"shape."
msgstr ""
"Če želite narisati pravokotnik s središčno točko po vaši izbiri, držite "
"&Ctrl;, kliknite središčno točko in povlecite, dokler ni pravokotnik "
"pravilne velikosti in oblike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To draw a square with a center point of your choice, hold &Ctrl; and "
"&Shift;, click on the center point, and drag until the square is the correct "
"size."
msgstr ""
"Če želite narisati kvadrat s središčem po vaši izbiri, držite &Ctrl; in "
"&Shift;, kliknite središčno točko in povlecite, dokler kvadrat ni pravilne "
"velikosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selections"
msgstr "Izbire"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the selection tools to draw out the boundary of a selection."
msgstr "Uporabite orodja za izbor, da narišete mejo izbora."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move the selection, click and drag on it. The main view will scroll as "
"required to allow you to move the selection to part of the image that is not "
"currently displayed."
msgstr ""
"Če želite premakniti izbor, ga kliknite in povlecite. Glavni pogled se bo "
"premikal po potrebi, da boste lahko premaknili izbor na del slike, ki "
"trenutno ni prikazan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can free-form <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Resize</link> the "
"entire image or <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Smooth Scale</link> the "
"selection using the corresponding handles. Hold &Shift; while free-form "
"scaling the selection to maintain aspect ratio. The &RMB; invokes a context "
"menu with common <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> commands and <link linkend=\"image-"
"effects-section\">Image Effects</link>."
msgstr ""
"Lahko prosto oblikujete <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Spremenite "
"velikost</link> celotne slike ali <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale"
"\">Gladko prilagodite</link> izbiro z uporabo ustreznih ročic . Držite "
"&Shift; medtem ko v prosti obliki prilagajate izbor, da ohranite razmerje "
"stranic. &RMB; prikliče kontekstni meni s pogostimi ukazi <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu> in <link linkend=\"image-effects-section\">učinki slike</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:735
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the cursor keys while drawing out the boundary of the selection "
"or while moving it."
msgstr ""
"Med risanjem meje izbora ali med premikanjem lahko uporabljate smerne tipke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you hold &Ctrl; before moving the selection, then you will move a copy of "
"it. The selection will be smeared when moving it while &Shift; is held."
msgstr ""
"Če držite &Ctrl; preden premaknete izbor, boste premaknili njegovo kopijo. "
"Izbor bo zamazan, ko ga premikate, medtem ko držite tipko &Shift;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two selection modes: Opaque (default) and Transparent. If you use "
"the Transparent selection mode, all pixels of the background color will be "
"transparent (background subtraction). This allows you to paste a selection "
"without the background. To perform background subtraction on a dithered "
"image, use a <link linkend=\"color-box\">Color Similarity</link> setting "
"other than Exact."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dva načina izbire: neprosojen (privzeto) in prosojen. Če "
"uporabljate način izbire Prosojen, bodo vse slikovne pike barve ozadja "
"prosojne (odštevanje ozadja). To vam omogoča, da prilepite izbor brez "
"ozadja. Če želite izvesti odštevanje ozadja na mehki sliki, uporabite "
"nastavitev <link linkend=\"color-box\">Podobnost barv</link>, ki ni Natančno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can apply Image Effects to a selection - see the <link linkend=\"image-"
"effects-section\">Image Effects</link> section for more information."
msgstr ""
"Za izbor lahko uporabite slikovne učinke – za več informacij glejte razdelek "
"<link linkend=\"image-effects-section\">Slikovni učinki</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to save selection to file using the <guimenuitem>Copy to "
"File...</guimenuitem> item from the selection context menu or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy to File...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> item from the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Izbor lahko shranite v datoteko z uporabo elementa <guimenuitem>Kopiraj v "
"datoteko...</guimenuitem> iz kontekstnega menija za izbiro ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kopiraj v datoteko...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v glavnem meniju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spraycan"
msgstr "Pršilka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to spray graffiti. Hold down the mouse button for a more "
"concentrated spray."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite in povlecite, da razpršite grafite. Držite tipko miške za bolj "
"koncentrirano pršilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the shapes to select the spray size. You can select from "
"spray sizes of 9x9, 17x17 and 29x29."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite eno od oblik, da izberete velikost razpršila. Izbirate lahko med "
"velikostmi pršil 9x9, 17x17 in 29x29."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:815
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag an area in which to write text. As soon as the border will be "
"shown you can start writing the text. Click and drag on the border to move "
"it. You can resize the text box by dragging on the handles or by using the "
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Resize</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite in povlecite območje, v katerega želite napisati besedilo. Takoj ko "
"se prikaže obroba, lahko začnete pisati besedilo. Kliknite in povlecite "
"obrobo, da jo premaknete. Velikost besedilnega polja lahko spremenite tako, "
"da povlečete ročice ali uporabite pogovorno okno <link linkend=\"image-"
"resize-scale\">Spremeni velikost</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have deselected a text box you can use <guimenuitem>Undo</"
"guimenuitem> to edit the text again."
msgstr ""
"Če ste preklicali izbiro besedilnega polja, lahko uporabite "
"<guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>, da znova uredite besedilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Transparent Color"
msgstr "Uporaba prosojne barve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left picture shows the example image. The right picture shows the "
"addition of text with opaque foreground and background colors."
msgstr ""
"Leva slika prikazuje primer slike. Desna slika prikazuje dodajanje besedila "
"z neprosojnimi barvami ospredja in ozadja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left picture shows the addition of text with opaque foreground colors "
"and a transparent background color. The right picture shows the addition of "
"text with a transparent foreground color and opaque background color."
msgstr ""
"Leva slika prikazuje dodajanje besedila z neprosojnimi barvami ospredja in "
"prozorno barvo ozadja. Desna slika prikazuje dodajanje besedila s prosojno "
"barvo ospredja in neprosojno barvo ozadja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom"
msgstr "Zoom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &LMB; zooms in. The &RMB; zooms out."
msgstr "&LMB; poveča. &RMB; pomanjša."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag with &LMB; to zoom into a specific area."
msgstr "Povlecite z &LMB; za povečavo določenega območja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid "Double click on the Zoom tool icon to set zoom to \"Fit to Page\"."
msgstr ""
"Dvokliknite ikono orodja za povečavo, da nastavite povečavo na \"Prilagodi "
"strani\"."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common Tool Options"
msgstr "Skupne možnosti orodja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the squares to select the eraser size. You can select from "
"squares of side length 2, 3, 5, 9, 17 and 29 pixels."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na enega od kvadratkov, da izberete velikost radirke. Izbirate "
"lahko med kvadrati s stranico 2, 3, 5, 9, 17 in 29 slikovnih pik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:899
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The eraser size setting affects the <link linkend=\"tool-erasers\">Erasers</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev velikosti radirke vpliva na <link linkend=\"tool-erasers"
"\">radirke</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the lines to select the line width. You can select from line "
"widths of 1, 2, 3, 5 and 8 pixel(s)."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na eno od vrstic, da izberete širino črte. Izbirate lahko med "
"širinami črt 1, 2, 3, 5 in 8 slikovnih pik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The line width setting affects the <link linkend=\"tool-polystar\">Connected "
"Lines</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-curve\">Curve</link>, <link linkend="
"\"tool-ellipse\">Ellipse</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-line\">Line</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"tool-polystar\">Polygon</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-"
"rectangles\">Rectangle</link> and <link linkend=\"tool-rectangles\">Rounded "
"Rectangle</link> tools."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev širine črte vpliva na <link linkend=\"tool-polystar\">povezane "
"črte</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-curve\">krivuljo</link>, <link linkend="
"\"tool-ellipse\">elipso </link>, <link linkend=\"tool-line\">črta</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"tool-polystar\">mnogokotnik</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-"
"rectangles\">pravokotnik</link> in orodji <link linkend=\"tool-rectangles"
"\">Zaobljen pravokotnik</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the rectangles to select the fill style. You can select from "
"No Fill, Fill with Background Color and Fill with Foreground Color."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na enega od pravokotnikov, da izberete slog polnila. Izbirate lahko "
"med možnostmi Brez polnila, Polnilo z barvo ozadja in Polnilo z barvo "
"ospredja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:936
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The fill style setting affects the <link linkend=\"tool-ellipse\">Ellipse</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"tool-polystar\">Polygon</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-"
"rectangles\">Rectangle</link> and <link linkend=\"tool-rectangles\">Rounded "
"Rectangle</link> tools."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev sloga polnila vpliva na <link linkend=\"tool-ellipse\">Elipso</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"tool-polystar\">Mnogokotnik</link>, <link linkend="
"\"tool-rectangles\">Pravokotnik</link> in <link linkend=\"tool-rectangles"
"\">zaobljen pravokotnik</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:952
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Working with Color</title>"
msgstr "<title>Delo z barvo</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:955
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Color Box"
msgstr "Škatla z barvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Box"
msgstr "Škatla z barvami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:968
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Color Box has 3 main sections: the Color Tablet, the Color Palette and "
"the Color Similarity Selector."
msgstr ""
"Škatla z barvami polje ima 3 glavne razdelke: barvno tablico, barvno paleto "
"in izbirnik podobnosti barv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:971
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Color Tablet shows the current foreground color as a square on top of "
"another square representing the current background color. When drawing with "
"the &LMB;, the foreground color is used, and when drawing with the &RMB; the "
"background color is used (except for the <link linkend=\"tool-erasers"
"\">Erasers</link>). You can click on the double-ended arrow to swap the "
"foreground and background colors."
msgstr ""
"Barvna tablica prikazuje trenutno barvo ospredja kot kvadrat na vrhu drugega "
"kvadrata, ki predstavlja trenutno barvo ozadja. Pri risanju z &LMB; se "
"uporablja barva ospredja, pri risanju z &RMB; uporabljena je barva ozadja "
"(razen za <link linkend=\"tool-erasers\">radirke</link>). Če želite "
"zamenjati barvo ospredja in ozadja, lahko kliknete puščico z dvojnim koncem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Color Palette shows a selection of colors for you to choose from. The "
"translucent pyramid represents the transparent color. Left-click on a color "
"to set the foreground color and right-click on a color to set the background "
"color. You can also drag and drop any opaque color into the Color Tablet "
"squares. To edit a color in the Color Tablet or Palette, double-click on it. "
"The <link linkend=\"tool-color-picker\">Color Picker</link> tool allows you "
"to select a color from the image."
msgstr ""
"Barvna paleta prikazuje izbor barv, med katerimi lahko izbirate. Prosojna "
"piramida predstavlja prozorno barvo. Z levim klikom na barvo nastavite barvo "
"ospredja in z desnim klikom na barvo nastavite barvo ozadja. Prav tako lahko "
"povlečete in spustite poljubno neprozorno barvo v kvadratke barvne tablice. "
"Če želite urediti barvo v barvni tablici ali paleti, dvokliknite nanjo. "
"Orodje <link linkend=\"tool-color-picker\">Izbirnik barv</link> omogoča "
"izbiro barve s slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Color Similarity allows you to work more effectively with dithered images "
"and photos, in a comparable manner to the <quote>Magic Wand</quote> feature "
"of other paint programs. It applies to transparent selections, as well as "
"the <link linkend=\"tool-flood-fill\">Flood Fill</link>, <link linkend="
"\"tool-eraser-clr\">Color Eraser</link> and <link linkend=\"image-autocrop"
"\">Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</link> tools. Double-click on the Color "
"Similarity Selector to choose how similar colors must be to be considered "
"identical. When using selections in Transparent mode, any color in the "
"selection that is similar to the background color will also be made "
"transparent."
msgstr ""
"Barvna podobnost vam omogoča učinkovitejše delo z mehkimi slikami in "
"fotografijami, podobno kot funkcija <quote>Čarobna paličica</quote> drugih "
"programov za slikanje. Velja za prosojne izbore, kot tudi za <link linkend="
"\"tool-flood-fill\">Poplavno polnilo</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-eraser-clr"
"\">Barvno radirko</link> in <link linkend=\"image-autocrop\">Orodja za "
"samodejno obrezovanje/Odstrani notranji rob</link>. Dvokliknite izbirnik "
"podobnosti barv, da izberete, kako podobne morajo biti barve, da veljajo za "
"enake. Pri uporabi izbir v prosojnem načinu bo prosojna tudi vsaka barva v "
"izboru, ki je podobna barvi ozadja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left picture shows the example image. The right pictures demonstrate the "
"use of a flood fill, with Color Similarity settings of 5%, 15% and 30%. In "
"this example, with a Color Similarity setting of <guilabel>Exact</guilabel>, "
"a flood fill at (80, 100) would only fill one pixel, as the surrounding "
"pixels are similar but not identical. As Color Similarity is increased, more "
"pixels that are similar in color are considered identical, hence the fill "
"extends further."
msgstr ""
"Leva slika prikazuje primer slike. Desne slike prikazujejo uporabo "
"poplavnega polnila z nastavitvami barvne podobnosti 5 %, 15 % in 30 %. V tem "
"primeru bi z nastavitvijo barvne podobnosti <guilabel>Natančno</guilabel> "
"poplavno polnjenje pri (80, 100) zapolnilo samo eno slikovno piko, saj so "
"okoliške slikovne pike podobne, vendar ne enake. Ko se poveča barvna "
"podobnost, se več slikovnih pik, ki so podobne barve, šteje za enakih, zato "
"se polnilo razširi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>View Options</title>"
msgstr "<title>Možnosti pogleda</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Options Reference"
msgstr "Oglejte si reference možnosti"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"view-zoom\">Zoom incorporating the Grid</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"view-zoom\">Povečava, ki vključuje mrežo</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1018
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"view-thumbnail\">Thumbnail</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"view-thumbnail\">Sličica</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Zoom incorporating the Grid</title>"
msgstr "<title>Povečava, ki vključuje mrežo</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1024
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increase the zoom level to edit images with more precision, or reduce it to "
"see more of the image."
msgstr ""
"Povečajte stopnjo povečave, če želite natančneje urejati slike, ali jo "
"zmanjšajte, če želite videti večji del slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At zoom levels that aren't multiples of 100%, parts of the image may appear "
"to move when the user interacts with it. Other minor redraw glitches may "
"also occur at such zoom levels."
msgstr ""
"Pri stopnjah povečave, ki niso večkratniki 100 %, se lahko zdi, da se deli "
"slike premikajo, ko uporabnik z njimi komunicira. Pri takih stopnjah "
"povečave se lahko pojavijo tudi druge manjše napake pri ponovnem risanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At zoom levels of 400% or greater that are also multiples of 100%, you can "
"<guimenuitem>Show Grid</guimenuitem> to more accurately edit individual "
"pixels."
msgstr ""
"Pri stopnjah povečave 400 % ali več, ki so tudi večkratniki 100 %, lahko "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži mrežo</guimenuitem> za natančnejše urejanje posameznih "
"slikovnih pik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first picture shows the <link linkend=\"tool-text\">Text</link> tool "
"icon, while the latter shows it at 600% zoom with the grid on."
msgstr ""
"Prva slika prikazuje ikono orodja <link linkend=\"tool-text\">Besedilo</"
"link>, druga pa jo prikazuje pri 600-odstotni povečavi z vklopljeno mrežo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way of zooming when not drawing is to scroll the <mousebutton>wheel</"
"mousebutton> while holding &Ctrl;."
msgstr ""
"Drug način povečave, ko ne rišete, je premikanje <mousebutton>kolesca</"
"mousebutton>, medtem ko držite &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1059
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Thumbnail</title>"
msgstr "<title>Sličica</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guimenuitem>Zoomed Thumbnail Mode</guimenuitem> is selected, the entire "
"image is displayed, scaled as required to fit the thumbnail window (top-"
"right picture)."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbran <guimenuitem>Način povečane sličice</guimenuitem>, je prikazana "
"celotna slika, po potrebi pomanjšana, da se prilega oknu s sličicami (slika "
"zgoraj desno)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Otherwise, the thumbnail displays as much of the image as possible, starting "
"from the top-left of the main view (bottom-right picture)."
msgstr ""
"V nasprotnem primeru sličica prikaže čim večji del slike, začenši od "
"zgornjega levega kota glavnega pogleda (slika spodaj desno)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Image Effects</title>"
msgstr "<title>Slikovni učinki</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image Effects Reference"
msgstr "Referenca slikovnih učinkov"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"image-autocrop\">Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"image-autocrop\">Samodejno obrezovanje/Odstrani notranji "
"rob</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-balance\">Balance</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-balance\">Uravnoteži</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1084
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-clear\">Clear</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-clear\">Počisti</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1085
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-emboss\">Emboss</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-emboss\">Vgraviraj</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-flatten\">Flatten</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-flatten\">Splošči</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-flip\">Flip (upside down)</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-flip\">Obrni (na glavo)</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1088
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-invert\">Invert</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-invert\">Obrni</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1089
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Reduce Colors</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Zmanjšaj barve</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-grayscale\">Reduce to Grayscale</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-grayscale\">Zmanjšaj v sivine</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"image-monochrome\">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"image-monochrome\">Zmanjšaj na enobarvno (zabrisano)</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-mirror\">Mirror (horizontally)</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-mirror\">Zrcaljenje (vodoravno)</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1093
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Resize / Scale</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Spreminjanje velikosti / merilo</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1094
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-rotate\">Rotate</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-rotate\">Zavrti</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1095
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-set-as-image\">Set as Image (Crop)</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-set-as-image\">Nastavi kot sliko (obreži)</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-skew\">Skew</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-skew\">Nagni</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-soften-sharpen\">Soften &amp; Sharpen</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-soften-sharpen\">Zmehčaj &amp; Izostri</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-more-effects\">More Effects</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-more-effects\">Več učinkov</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1099
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-notes\">Notes</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-notes\">Opombe</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</title>"
msgstr "<title>Samodejno obrezovanje / Odstrani notranjo obrobo</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This automatically removes the border of an image or selection. Use Autocrop "
"if you have a figure that does not fill the entire image or selection and "
"you wish to remove the excess whitespace. To use this feature with a "
"dithered image border, you will also need to use <link linkend=\"color-box"
"\">Color Similarity</link>."
msgstr ""
"To samodejno odstrani obrobo slike ali izbora. Uporabite samodejno obreži, "
"če imate figuro, ki ne zapolni celotne slike ali izbora in želite odstraniti "
"odvečni prazen prostor. Če želite uporabiti to funkcijo z mešano obrobo "
"slike, boste morali uporabiti tudi <link linkend=\"color-box\">Podobnost "
"barv</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Balance</title>"
msgstr "<title>Uravnoteži</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1116 index.docbook:1154 index.docbook:1174 index.docbook:1200
#: index.docbook:1234 index.docbook:1387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature is accessible from the <link linkend=\"image-more-effects"
"\">More Effects</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija je dostopna v pogovornem oknu <link linkend=\"image-more-effects"
"\">Več učinkov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to set the brightness, contrast and gamma of the image or "
"selection."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča nastavitev svetlosti, kontrasta in gama slike ali izbora."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The more common measure of gamma (a decimal from 0.10 to 10.00) is located "
"between the <guilabel>Gamma</guilabel> spinbox and the <guibutton>Reset</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Pogostejša mera gama (decimalna številka od 0,10 do 10,00) se nahaja med "
"vrtilnim poljem <guilabel>Gama</guilabel> in gumbom <guibutton>Ponastavi</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Clear</title>"
msgstr "<title>Počisti</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1141
#, no-c-format
msgid "This fills the entire image or selection with the background color."
msgstr "To zapolni celotno sliko ali izbor z barvo ozadja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click on the <link linkend=\"tool-eraser-std\">Eraser</link> icon to "
"clear the entire image."
msgstr ""
"Dvokliknite ikono <link linkend=\"tool-eraser-std\">Radirke</link>, da "
"počistite celotno sliko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Emboss</title>"
msgstr "<title>Vgraviraj</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> to apply the Emboss effect. This "
"emphasises the edges and gives the image or selection an &quot;engraved "
"look&quot;."
msgstr ""
"Označite <guilabel>Omogoči</guilabel>, da uporabite učinek vgraviranja. To "
"poudari robove in daje sliki ali izboru &quot;vgraviran videz&quot;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Flatten</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošči</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "This recolors the image with varying shades of the two selected colors."
msgstr "To prebarva sliko z različnimi odtenki dveh izbranih barv."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Flip (upside down)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Obrni (na glavo)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid "This flips the entire image or selection vertically."
msgstr "To obrne celotno sliko ali izbor navpično."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Invert</title>"
msgstr "<title>Obrni</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to invert one or more RGB channels in the image or "
"selection. Select <guilabel>All</guilabel> to change a photo into a negative "
"and vice versa. This generally looks quite funny."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča, da obrnete enega ali več kanalov RGB na sliki ali izboru. "
"Izberite <guilabel>Vse</guilabel>, da spremenite fotografijo v negativ in "
"obratno. To je na splošno videti precej smešno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To quickly invert all channels, you do not need to use this dialog. You can "
"instead access the <guimenuitem>Invert Colors</guimenuitem> item in the "
"<guimenu>Image</guimenu> or <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> menu. The "
"<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> item is only displayed in the menubar if you "
"use one of the selection tools. Additionally you can reach this action from "
"the context menu opened with a &RMB; click in the image area."
msgstr ""
"Če želite hitro obrniti vse kanale, vam ni treba uporabiti tega pogovornega "
"okna. Namesto tega lahko dostopate do elementa <guimenuitem>Obrni barve</"
"guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> ali <guimenu>Izbira</"
"guimenu>. Element <guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> je prikazan v menijski vrstici "
"samo, če uporabljate eno od izbirnih orodij. Poleg tega lahko to dejanje "
"dosežete iz kontekstnega menija, ki ga odprete z &RMB; kliknite v območju "
"slike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Mirror (horizontally)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zrcalo (vodoravno)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid "This mirrors the entire image or selection horizontally."
msgstr "To vodoravno prezrcali celotno sliko ali izbor."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Reduce Colors</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zmanjšaj barve</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This reduces the number of colors used by the image or selection, with or "
"without dithering."
msgstr ""
"To zmanjša število barv, ki jih uporablja slika ali izbor, z mehčanjem ali "
"brez njega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dithering generally provides better quality results, however, you may wish "
"to disable it for artistic effects; &eg; using <guilabel>Monochrome</"
"guilabel> instead of <guilabel>Monochrome (Dithered)</guilabel> gives a "
"silhouette effect."
msgstr ""
"Zmehčanje na splošno zagotavlja boljšo kakovost rezultatov, vendar ga boste "
"morda želeli onemogočiti za umetniške učinke; &eg; uporaba "
"<guilabel>Enobarvno</guilabel> namesto <guilabel>Enobarvno (Zmehčano)</"
"guilabel> daje učinek silhuete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another important distinction is that while <guilabel>Monochrome (Dithered)</"
"guilabel> will always reduce the entire image or selection to black and "
"white, <guilabel>Monochrome</guilabel> will do this only if the image or "
"selection contains more than 2 colors."
msgstr ""
"Druga pomembna razlika je, da medtem ko bo <guilabel>Enobarvno (zmehčano)</"
"guilabel> celotno sliko ali izbor vedno zmanjšal na črno-belo, bo "
"<guilabel>Enobarvno</guilabel> to storil le, če slika ali izbor vsebuje več "
"kot 2 barvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a quick, dithered monochrome image or selection, use the <link linkend="
"\"image-monochrome\">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</link> item of the "
"<guimenu>Image</guimenu> or <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> menu. The "
"<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> item is only displayed in the menubar if you "
"use one of the selection tools. Additionally you can reach this action from "
"the context menu opened with a &RMB; click in the image area."
msgstr ""
"Za hitro mehčano enobarvno sliko ali izbor uporabite element <link linkend="
"\"image-monochrome\">Zmanjšaj v enobarvno (zmehčano)</link> v "
"<guimenu>Slika</guimenu> ali <guimenu>Izbor</guimenu> meni. Element "
"<guimenu>Izbira</guimenu> je prikazan v menijski vrstici samo, če "
"uporabljate eno od izbirnih orodij. Poleg tega lahko to dejanje dosežete iz "
"kontekstnega menija, ki ga odprete z &RMB; kliknite v območju slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the number of colors here has no effect on the color depth of the "
"file format. If you want to change the color depth, you should select it in "
"the file saving dialogs. Note that, confusingly, changing the color depth "
"also changes the number of colors."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje števila barv tukaj ne vpliva na barvno globino zapisa datoteke. "
"Če želite spremeniti globino barve, jo izberite v pogovornih oknih za "
"shranjevanje datotek. Upoštevajte, da sprememba globine barve spremeni tudi "
"število barv, kar je zavajajoče."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Reduce to Grayscale</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zmanjšaj v sivine</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid "This reduces the entire image or selection to grayscale."
msgstr "To zmanjša celotno sliko ali izbor na sivine."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zmanjšaj na enobarvno (zmehčano)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid "This reduces the entire image or selection to black and white."
msgstr "To zmanjša celotno sliko ali izbor na črno-belo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not want the image or selection to be dithered, use the <link "
"linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\"> Reduce Colors</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite, da je slika ali izbor mehča, uporabite pogovorno okno <link "
"linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\"> Zmanjšaj barve</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Resize / Scale</title>"
msgstr "<title>Spreminjanje velikosti / merilo</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resizing the image changes the dimensions of the image without applying a "
"transformation to the existing contents. Scaling the image will stretch the "
"existing contents to the new dimensions. <guibutton>Smooth Scale</guibutton> "
"generally provides better quality results than Scaling, by blending "
"neighbouring colors."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje velikosti slike spremeni dimenzije slike brez uporabe "
"transformacije obstoječe vsebine. Povečanje velikosti slike bo raztegnilo "
"obstoječo vsebino na nove dimenzije. <guibutton>Gladka skala</guibutton> na "
"splošno zagotavlja boljšo kakovost rezultatov kot skaliranje z mešanjem "
"sosednjih barv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can express the new dimensions in pixels, or as a percentage of the "
"original size. If you select <guilabel>Keep aspect ratio</guilabel>, the "
"width and height will be scaled by the same percentage."
msgstr ""
"Nove dimenzije lahko izrazite v slikovnih pikah ali kot odstotek prvotne "
"velikosti. Če izberete <guilabel>Ohrani razmerje stranic</guilabel>, bosta "
"širina in višina pomanjšani za enak odstotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can free-form <guibutton>Resize</guibutton> the entire image or "
"<guibutton>Smooth Scale</guibutton> the selection using the corresponding "
"handles."
msgstr ""
"Lahko prosto oblikujete <guibutton>Spremeni velikost</guibutton> celotne "
"slike ali <guibutton>Smooth Scale</guibutton> izbor z uporabo ustreznih "
"ročic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only scaling is supported for selections, and only resizing is supported for "
"text boxes. See <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Notes</link> for additional "
"details about applying these effects."
msgstr ""
"Za izbore je podprto samo spreminjanje velikosti, za besedilna polja pa samo "
"spreminjanje velikosti. Glejte <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Opombe</link> "
"za dodatne podrobnosti o uporabi teh učinkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Rotate</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zavrti</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This rotates the image. You can specify the angle and direction of rotation."
msgstr "To obrne sliko. Določite lahko kot in smer vrtenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reverse the direction of rotation by specifying a negative custom "
"angle."
msgstr "Smer vrtenja lahko obrnete tako, da določite negativni kot po meri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348 index.docbook:1379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Notes</link> for details about applying "
"this effect to a selection."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Opombe</link> za podrobnosti o uporabi "
"tega učinka za izbor."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1355
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Set as Image (Crop)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Nastavi kot sliko (obreži)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will set the selection as the image."
msgstr "To bo nastavilo izbiro kot sliko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1360
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is only available when you have an active selection."
msgstr "To je na voljo le, če imate aktivno izbiro."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Skew</title>"
msgstr "<title>Nagni</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This skews the entire image or selection horizontally and/or vertically."
msgstr "To nagne celotno sliko ali izbor vodoravno in/ali navpično."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Soften &amp; Sharpen</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zmehčaj &amp; Izostri</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use this effect to soften or sharpen the image."
msgstr "S tem učinkom zmehčate ali izostrite sliko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>More Effects</title>"
msgstr "<title>Več učinkov</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog contains the <link linkend=\"image-balance\">Balance</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"image-emboss\">Emboss</link>, <link linkend=\"image-flatten"
"\">Flatten</link>, <link linkend=\"image-invert\">Invert</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Reduce Colors</link> and <link linkend="
"\"image-soften-sharpen\">Soften &amp; Sharpen</link> features."
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno vsebuje <link linkend=\"image-balance\">Ravnotežje</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"image-emboss\">Emboss</link>, <link linkend=\"image-flatten"
"\">Splošči</link >, <link linkend=\"image-invert\">Obrni</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Zmanjšaj barve</link> in <link linkend="
"\"image-soften-sharpen\">Zmehčaj &amp; Izostri</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1417
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Notes</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opombe</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Resizing / Scaling</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"image-rotate\">Rotating</link> and <link linkend=\"image-skew"
"\">Skewing</link> may change the dimensions of the image. You can view the "
"new dimensions in the dialog."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Spreminjanje velikosti / lestvica</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"image-rotate\">Vrtenje</link> in <link linkend="
"\"image-skew\">Poševno spreminjanje</link > lahko spremeni dimenzije slike. "
"Nove dimenzije si lahko ogledate v pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you apply these effects to an image, the image will be resized if "
"necessary. However, if you apply these effects to a selection, the image "
"will not be resized, even if the transformed selection does not fit."
msgstr ""
"Če te učinke uporabite na sliki, bo slika po potrebi spremenjena. Če pa te "
"učinke uporabite za izbor, se velikost slike ne bo spremenila, tudi če se "
"preoblikovani izbor ne prilega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left image has been rotated 30 degrees clockwise to form the right "
"image. &kolourpaint; has automatically enlarged the image to accommodate the "
"larger contents."
msgstr ""
"Leva slika je bila zasukana za 30 stopinj v smeri urinega kazalca, da se "
"oblikuje desna slika. &kolourpaint; je samodejno povečal sliko, da se "
"prilagodi večji vsebini."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left <emphasis>selection</emphasis> has been rotated 30 degrees "
"clockwise to form the right selection. The image size has remained the same, "
"hence parts of the selection will not be visible without <link linkend="
"\"image-resize-scale\">Resizing</link> the <emphasis>image</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Levi <emphasis>izbor</emphasis> je bil zasukan za 30 stopinj v smeri urinega "
"kazalca, da se oblikuje desni izbor. Velikost slike je ostala enaka, zato "
"deli izbora ne bodo vidni, če <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale"
"\">spremenite velikost</link> <emphasis>slike</emphasis>."

